import React from 'react'

import {Container, Row, Col, Card, CardColumns, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'

const CardPost = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <CardColumns>
                <Col sm>                
                    <Card className="p-2">
                        <Card.Img 
                            variant="top" 
                            src="https://st.depositphotos.com/1780879/3816/i/600/depositphotos_38166573-stock-photo-trees-with-sunbeams.jpg"
                        />
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Postagem</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                                Texto exemplo dentro do Card
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary">Leia Mais</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                        <Card.Footer>
                            <small className="text-muted">
                                Última atualização 3 minutos atras
                            </small>
                        </Card.Footer>
                    </Card>
                </Col>
                <Col sm>                
                    <Card className="p-2">
                        <Card.Img 
                            variant="top" 
                            src="https://st.depositphotos.com/1780879/3816/i/600/depositphotos_38166573-stock-photo-trees-with-sunbeams.jpg"
                        />
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Postagem</Card.Title>

                            </small>

                        <Card.Img 
                            variant="top" 
                            src="https://st.depositphotos.com/1780879/3816/i/600/depositphotos_38166573-stock-photo-trees-with-sunbeams.jpg"
                        />
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Postagem</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                                Texto exemplo dentro do Card
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary">Leia Mais</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                        <Card.Footer>
                            <small className="text-muted">
                                Última atualização 3 minutos atras
                            </small>
                        </Card.Footer>
                    </Card>
                </Col>
                <Col sm>                
                    <Card className="p-2">
                        <Card.Img 
                            variant="top" 
                            src="https://st.depositphotos.com/1780879/3816/i/600/depositphotos_38166573-stock-photo-trees-with-sunbeams.jpg"
                        />
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Postagem</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                                Texto exemplo dentro do Card
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary">Leia Mais</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                        <Card.Footer>
                            <small className="text-muted">
                                Última atualização 3 minutos atras
                            </small>
                        </Card.Footer>
                    </Card>
                </Col>
            </CardColumns>
        </>
    )
}

const Posts = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <CardPost/>
                </Row>
            </Container>

        </>
    )
}

export default Posts
